.Dd June 2, 2026
.Dt SP 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sp
.Nd print formatted song metadata
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar format
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
reads paths or song references from standard input, expands paths to Matroska
chapters, and writes one formatted line per song to standard output.
.Pp
A song reference has the form
.Ar path Ns # Ns Ar chapter-id .
.Sh FORMAT
Literal text is copied to the output.
Fields are written as
.Cm { Ns Ar field Ns Cm } .
Available fields are
.Cm {date} ,
.Cm {orig-date} ,
.Cm {artist} ,
.Cm {title} ,
.Cm {genre} ,
.Cm {album} ,
.Cm {#} ,
and
.Cm {disc} .
Use a backslash to quote the next character.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr sf 1 ,
.Xr so 1
